Package ca.ualberta.cs.funtime_runtime.thread

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddAccountThread
    This thread is used to add an Account made locally and store it on the server
    AddQuestionThread
    Thread used to add a question created locally to the server
    SearchAccountThread
    Thread used to search the server for existing accounts, mainly used for Login and Create Account checking to prevent repeat accounts
    SearchActivityThread
    Thread used specifically for populating the search activity list
    SearchQuestionThread
    Thread that does a general load of server questions for local viewing
    UpdateAccountThread
    Thread used to update account information via ESAccountManager, used any time the user does a meaningful action in the application
    UpdateQuestionThread
    Thread that updates a question, done after an answer or reply is added, uses ESQuestionManager to do these updates
